data.description: A sophisticated design boasting customization and quality in an excellent location. If you are looking for something original and high quality, take a look at these quartz counter tops, custom ceilings, windows, interior sliding barn doors, and wooden beams in the living room to name a few notable additions. This modern stucco home also has modern fixtures and fans. It is nestled in a gated community near major streets, entertainment, and shopping centers: and up and coming growth. Enjoy the patio and large backyard (fully fenced). Don't forget the convenience of the garage. As a relatively new home, be assured the life of major factors such as the AC and Roof are in excellent shape. Sprinkler system equipped. This is an excellent forever home, starter home, or investment in a booming location that will surely be a smart purchase.
